b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2146,8015,47041,91957,134321],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"从一年级的看图说话开始就不会，根本不知道怎么组织语言，一句话都没法自己写不出来。不止是作文，阅读理解方面，只要遇到要用自己语言概括的都不行。每次考试，语文基础分基本都不扣，就是遇到阅读理解和作文就不行。给孩子请了老师一对一教作文，也没有什么成效，我们现在只能让他多背范文。 感觉孩子也不是不努力，就是没有开放性思维。数学，英语这些有标准答案的，他都没问题。他就是做不了自由发挥的题～"},"attached_info":"Cj4I9+zI0sDusr0sEAMaCDc5NTQ5MzMxIMv52ZIGMAA4TUAwcgk1Mjc3MDMwNTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"65 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-e615400b7cba5efe79be135d164f6fa9_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"49_1650273109.7291586","card_id":"Q_528586320","target":{"id":528586320,"title":"当今社会学历真的比自身能力重要吗?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/528586320","type":"question","created":1650240248,"answer_count":83,"follower_count":108,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[8634,10267,45437],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4I9+zI0sDusr0sEAMaCDc5NzQ1NTUyIPjV8pIGMAA4bEAxcgk1Mjg1ODYzMjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"65 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-a7b2c70ce2769b3a662227e64edab249_b.jpg"}]}],"description":{"time":"2022-04-18 17:11:50"}}